milestones.description: Khaled Mashud and Hasibul Hossain's 44-run partnership is BAN's highest for the 9th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 26 between Sheikh Salahuddin and Mafizur Rahman
Minhajul Abedin has broken the record for most ducks (3) in ODIs for BAN, going past Harunur Rashid's 2
Mohammad Rafique has become the top wicket-taker for BAN in ODIs with 15 wickets, going past Hasibul Hossain's 13
Aminul Islam has broken the record for most catches (7) in ODIs for BAN, going past Akram Khan's 6
